{"tid":409081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVBS新聞：加州喊獨立Calexit　推2019年公投","createTime":"2017-09-21T18:05:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T16:44:06.000Z","uid":47714,"like":25,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dd9f0e60ba20a4b272a09d2fb9840015e76dc6e6","tid":409081,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T18:05:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/685739\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvbs.com.tw%2Fworld%2F685739&d=W1WxbgH0RYfz0PpohfV0oP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=251585b8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvbs.com.tw/world/685739</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cc.tvbs.com.tw/img/upload/2016/11/10/20161110165322-74f8e421.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fimg%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F10%2F20161110165322-74f8e421.jpg&h=ac39ee4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨總統候選人川普勝選，民主黨最大票倉加州有支持者架設網頁，宣揚加州獨立公投，並力推於2019年投票決定是否脫離美國。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://YesCalifornia.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FYesCalifornia.org&d=W1WxbgH0RYfz0PpohfV0oP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b6f25338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">YesCalifornia.org</a>網站聲稱，支持加州獨立者，計劃在2019年春天舉辦歷史性的獨立公投，並且效法Brexit（英國脫歐）詞彙，訂定這項脫離美國的公投名為「Calexit」。<br />\n<br />\n支持加州獨立者主張，加州是世界第6大經濟體，經濟實力超越法國，並且人口比波蘭多，加州堪比他國並可與各國競爭，與美國其它49州不同。<br />\n<br />\n獨立倡議者更說，他們認為，美國代表的許多意義違反加州的價值，而且加州也持續如國家一般，資助其他許多州，而損及加州與加州的孩童權益。<br />\n<br />\n他們更聲稱，這個獨立公投的意義與重要性在於自決，以及依據憲法與國際法規範的自治概念，重要性更超越僅因資助這個國家其他州的考量。<br />\n<br />\n他們更相信，加州以國家地位參與這個世界後，更可以發揮加州的影響力，且加州成為獨立國家，可更勝於只是美國的一個州而已。"},{"pid":"c96d4f345572d1df7060545a5cc9ca223bb098ba","tid":409081,"uid":82929,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:29:30.000Z","msg":"等睇支那對美國內政，說三道四"},{"pid":"4bdd08644d627430064abcd84b980cbe890a12ae","tid":409081,"uid":8048,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:31:41.000Z","msg":"堅持一個美國原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8bd8acbd8f1ba49f4e9ee234d26faaa384b05f","tid":409081,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:34:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df333f4426484a41d72bc58eb8cc6e3afd321aef","tid":409081,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:35:48.000Z","msg":"美國警察開槍未？"},{"pid":"67110d506a208375946160b29645ee55e7c4a31b","tid":409081,"uid":52946,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:36:28.000Z","msg":"5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲"},{"pid":"167f57a7e8c0418416209e1004f6000c2d4e2de2","tid":409081,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:36:58.000Z","msg":"條友一次推三個post"},{"pid":"383630f091db196ec4d56eaec97675d5d5c760d4","tid":409081,"uid":135408,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:37:57.000Z","msg":"唔太明"},{"pid":"8712615a492d8f4b0dc8c9ee6da642324fcf31eb","tid":409081,"uid":19542,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:41:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系"},{"pid":"fe938293e42ba02f6663cc85a60feb0140496507","tid":409081,"uid":34666,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T23:47:10.000Z","msg":"加州獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇吓班係其他州登記自己部柴油私家車既車主放唔放過班左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b47641d33562f564ff20aaa4e791b8ece01efc5","tid":409081,"uid":56123,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:01:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個州都有國民警衛軍，由州長指揮<br />\n<br />\n而且每個州本身就係一個國家，各州都有自己法律，人地係先有個州，先至有美國，所以英文叫united states，即係一堆states聯合。各州會交左一啲權力由聯邦負責，其餘冇話交的權力全部歸返州政府<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果美國啲州話要獨立都幾麻煩，人地話依家唔再玩聯合都冇符，不過好似獨立要其餘既州都同意。好似係，歡迎指正"},{"pid":"f26b688589de47cf39a6e2e78114918e888d811f","tid":409081,"uid":37666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩fallout"},{"pid":"971d9cf8117ffd02f1b871410c50f296f61e00b2","tid":409081,"uid":67168,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩fallout</blockquote><br />\nNCR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a191cd1194bdae09d1d268564f6bbfdd07581f","tid":409081,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"咁大愛，記得到時收晒啲難民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b216be462b0fc56f35a9f2c672aa771fcd829887","tid":409081,"uid":57786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:08:11.000Z","msg":"係美國攪茉莉花<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ba993552376a6e4e8edc49225df53fb58e23a6","tid":409081,"uid":105352,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:12:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3657f4fd030ab1c242f3b5f0aeceea45c6f6973","tid":409081,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n每個州都有國民警衛軍，由州長指揮<br />\n<br />\n而且每個州本身就係一個國家，各州都有自己法律，人地係先有個州，先至有美國，所以英文叫united states，即係一堆states聯合。各州會交左一啲權力由聯邦負責，其餘冇話交的權力全部歸返州政府<br />\n<br />\n所以，如果美國啲州話要獨立都幾麻煩，人地話依家唔再玩聯合都冇符，不過好似獨立要其餘既州都同意。好似係，歡迎指正</blockquote><br />\n南北戰爭嗰次咪試過囉，比起加州呢次仲大陣仗添，軍力更強，一樣失敗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c11a80f9403fc591e97f4a3b0bb7723e0f3e1d","tid":409081,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"首先話因為經濟要引入移民<br />\n跟著移民多就話要包容其他文化<br />\n最後就話文化同其他地方唔同而要獨立<br />\n咁你玩鳩哂啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaca24ced39c1d9989ddc339e0f1c99a2ef7e84","tid":409081,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先話因為經濟要引入移民<br />\n跟著移民多就話要包容其他文化<br />\n最後就話文化同其他地方唔同而要獨立<br />\n咁你玩鳩哂啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左膠思想殘害世界"},{"pid":"8e8969afa480d3e2b4db756d6392dd3351b095c4","tid":409081,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>首先話因為經濟要引入移民<br />\n跟著移民多就話要包容其他文化<br />\n最後就話文化同其他地方唔同而要獨立<br />\n咁你玩鳩哂啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n左膠思想殘害世界</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加州依家都係左膠典範黎架啦"},{"pid":"1caf9af4f82b9912e21c44ca5d199e64415d1309","tid":409081,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:38:17.000Z","msg":"美國左膠玩嘢者"},{"pid":"922f776fb01ea39fa19f9e97d7c2f1430680081e","tid":409081,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:43:31.000Z","msg":"獨立要2/3州份同意"},{"pid":"78d79acc8c63a00034ecb9cf6ad8c7688e494d45","tid":409081,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"608e171c3e495853e8c5dfb8b87c949b19faa02a","tid":409081,"uid":21249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T00:56:51.000Z","msg":"加字頭又嗌獨立 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde8428ecb