98d9b405a6f46945a2e62992c07","tid":409081,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:37:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩fallout</blockquote><br />\n我最記得係第二代既NCR<br />\n<br />\n入面d警察既標準配備係M72高斯步槍<br />\n<br />\n火力好強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新維加斯個時班人好串<br />\n最後都係幫豪斯先生"},{"pid":"6745d8c354e0af3a3fe4bb9413e2cdc7ef86a2d9","tid":409081,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"仲天荒夜談過港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83aab7fae1a59e0457f6e91cb58aed3400950239","tid":409081,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:42:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/134205_67dc20b2ffeb896ce01141430c43c4a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F134205_67dc20b2ffeb896ce01141430c43c4a3.png&h=21f65d8e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img00.deviantart.net/2225/i/2015/221/a/5/ncr_money_by_istabhotlava-d94zkvn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg00.deviantart.net%2F2225%2Fi%2F2015%2F221%2Fa%2F5%2Fncr_money_by_istabhotlava-d94zkvn.jpg&h=16921792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n錢都印埋啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6f9b7bbe5890dad98357201c592b60b94a5d03","tid":409081,"uid":60529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T12:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>5毛：加洲有冇軍隊先 水電食物都要靠其他洲</blockquote><br />\n認真 每個州都好似有軍隊 加州水電都可以靠自己<br />\n仲有加州係全球第六大經濟體系</blockquote><br />\n有冇玩fallout</blockquote><br />\n我最記得係第二代既NCR<br />\n<br />\n入面d警察既標準配備係M72高斯步槍<br />\n<br />\n火力好強 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n新維加斯個時班人好串<br />\n最後都係幫豪斯先生</blockquote><br />\nMr. House 都係一個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb06ae167cb46af93a1c1e927729e74fcc56f99c","tid":409081,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:01:56.000Z","msg":"獨立到應該德州都會獨立"},{"pid":"e58a9f432c927f509ec6255d4024599a4a8b5de9","tid":409081,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加州如果獨立左，民主黨更加無可能再選到總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"74eeae0dde7048d607d1b45cf1467a69300dcf9e","tid":409081,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:15:39.000Z","msg":"獨立公投都搞緊<br />\n曾鈺成哩啲垃圾仲好意思攞成百鳩幾年前既事抺黑美國<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯南北戰爭過後，美國最高法院1869年對「德州訴懷特案」(Texas v. White，下稱「德案」)的裁決，成為支持林肯「憲法禁止獨立」論的主要法理依據。德案爭論的問題，是德克薩斯州政府在南北戰爭期間發出的債券是否有效？當時德州已宣布脫離了合眾國，債券是按德州自行制訂的法規發出，並不符合美利堅合眾國的法律。所以，如果德州脫離合眾國的行為是合法的，債券便有效；否則債券必須作廢。法院裁定，德州脫離合眾國是違憲的；它脫離了合眾國所做的事，在法律上都是無效的。按法院判詞對美國憲法的解釋，合眾國是永久的、不可分割的。<br />\n<br />\n有意見認為，法院對德案的裁決，是考慮政治多於法理：難道法院可以宣布，南北戰爭打錯了，七十多萬美國人枉死了？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">到處支持人民自決的美國，並不容許自己的各州自決</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/不能妥協-96578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%A6%A5%E5%8D%94-96578&d=W1WxbgH0RYfz0PpohfV0oP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=9cbda419\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/column/新聞/不能妥協-96578</a><br />\n<br />\n面皮成尺厚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64562c20c4937b4ae43924f99b782a2d681f12d","tid":409081,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯 會唔會借機搞搞震, 出兵幫加州獨立??"},{"pid":"4754d956dc94480da9a154e8e0c4b5a6ec8074da","tid":409081,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a682a4bce7a4b09d4f9eba32e267dcad52a6a3db","tid":409081,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/134205_67dc20b2ffeb896ce01141430c43c4a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F134205_67dc20b2ffeb896ce01141430c43c4a3.png&h=21f65d8e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df45fbe20ebadb386efcf7368898f9cdca0f9102","tid":409081,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加州如果獨立左，民主黨更加無可能再選到總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n50張人票冇左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"612d638b3f765057c3aa3607adc34b9a54de3c12","tid":409081,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:25:31.000Z","msg":"apple 公司係加州，美國會唔會比佢獨立？"}]}